DROP TABLE FINANCE.BBBL2PT
#WARNING#
Non è possibile eliminare l'oggetto 'FINANCE.BBBL2PT' di tipo tabella, perché inesistente o perché non si dispone dell'autorizzazione.


CREATE TABLE FINANCE.BBBL2PT
(
   T01CD CHAR(3) NOT NULL,
   T64COPBC CHAR(6) NOT NULL,
   BILCD CHAR(10) NOT NULL,
   BNICD CHAR(5) NOT NULL,
   DIZSTATO CHAR(1),
   DIZNPROG NUMERIC(3,0) NOT NULL,
   BCTESTO VARCHAR(4000)
)  ON 'FINANCE8'
ALTER TABLE FINANCE.BBBL2PT ADD CONSTRAINT BBBL2PT_IX PRIMARY KEY (T01CD, T64COPBC, BILCD, BNICD, DIZNPROG )
GRANT ALL ON FINANCE.BBBL2PT TO PUBLIC
DROP TABLE FINANCE.BCBILDPT
#WARNING#
Non è possibile eliminare l'oggetto 'FINANCE.BCBILDPT' di tipo tabella, perché inesistente o perché non si dispone dell'autorizzazione.

(

   T64COPBC CHAR(6) NOT NULL,
   BILCD CHAR(10) NOT NULL,
   DIZSTATO CHAR(1),
   T33CD CHAR(3) NOT NULL,
   DIZDESLI CHAR(35),
   DIZDRILI CHAR(15)
)  ON 'FINANCE4'
ALTER TABLE FINANCE.BCBILDPT ADD CONSTRAINT BCBILDPT_IX PRIMARY KEY (T01CD, T64COPBC, BILCD, T33CD )
GRANT ALL ON FINANCE.BCBILDPT TO PUBLIC
DROP TABLE FINANCE.BCBILPT
#WARNING#
Non è possibile eliminare l'oggetto 'FINANCE.BCBILPT' di tipo tabella, perché inesistente o perché non si dispone dell'autorizzazione.


CREATE TABLE FINANCE.BCBILPT
(
   T01CD CHAR(3) NOT NULL,
   DIZSTATO CHAR(1),
   DIZUTCRE CHAR(8),
   DIZDTCRE DATETIME,
   DIZHHCRE DATETIME,
   DIZUTAGG CHAR(8),
   DIZDTAGG DATETIME,
   DIZHHAGG DATETIME,
   BILDSNOR CHAR(35),
   BILDSRID CHAR(15),
   BILDSRIC CHAR(15),
   BILDTINI DATETIME,
   BILDTFIN DATETIME,
   T64COPBC CHAR(6) NOT NULL,
   BILCD CHAR(10) NOT NULL,
   BAVTPBIL CHAR(1),
   BAVNRREA CHAR(20),
   BAVFOGIU CHAR(20),
   BAVDENCG CHAR(35),
   BAVNAZCG CHAR(35),
   BAVDENDI CHAR(35),
   WBSNRLOG NUMERIC(9,0),
   WPBNRLOG NUMERIC(9,0),
   ATTNE2 CHAR(70),
   BAVAPPGR CHAR(1),
   BAVSOLIQ CHAR(1),
   BAVSOUNI CHAR(1),
   BAVALDIR CHAR(1),
   ATTNEB CHAR(70),
   T96CD CHAR(8),
   SBCCSDBC CHAR(3)
)  ON 'FINANCE4'
ALTER TABLE FINANCE.BCBILPT ADD CONSTRAINT BCBILPT_IX PRIMARY KEY (T01CD, T64COPBC, BILCD )
GRANT ALL ON FINANCE.BCBILPT TO PUBLIC
DROP TABLE FINANCE.BCBL1PT

DROP VIEW FINANCE.BBBL2VA 
#WARNING#
Non è possibile eliminare l'oggetto 'FINANCE.BBBL2VA' di tipo vista, perché inesistente o perché non si dispone dell'autorizzazione.


CREATE VIEW FINANCE.BBBL2VA AS
SELECT
    T1.T01CD,
    T1.T64COPBC,
    T1.BILCD,
    T1.BNICD,
    T1.DIZSTATO,
    T1.DIZNPROG,
    T1.BCTESTO
FROM FINANCE.BBBL2PT T1

DROP VIEW FINANCE.BBBL2VL

    T1.T01CD,

DROP VIEW FINANCE.BCBILV2 
#WARNING#
Non è possibile eliminare l'oggetto 'FINANCE.BCBILV2' di tipo vista, perché inesistente o perché non si dispone dell'autorizzazione.


CREATE VIEW FINANCE.BCBILV2 (
    T01CD,
    DIZSTATO,
    DIZUTCRE,
    DIZDTCRE,
    DIZHHCRE,
    DIZUTAGG,
    DIZDTAGG,
    DIZHHAGG,
    BILDSNOR,
    BILDSRID,
    BILDSRIC,
    BILDTINI,
    BILDTFIN,
    T64COPBC,
    T64DESNO,
    T64DSRID,
    BILCD,
    BAVTPBIL,
    BAVNRREA,
    BAVFOGIU,
    BAVDENCG,
    BAVNAZCG,
    BAVDENDI,
    WBSNRLOG,
    WPBNRLOG,
    ATTNE2,
    BAVAPPGR,
    BAVSOLIQ,
    BAVSOUNI,
    BAVALDIR,
    ATTNEB,
    T96CD,
    SBCCSDBC,
    SBCDSNOR,
    SBCDSRID
) AS

SELECT
    T1.T01CD,
    T1.DIZSTATO,
    T1.DIZUTCRE,
    T1.DIZDTCRE,
    T1.DIZHHCRE,
    T1.DIZUTAGG,
    T1.DIZDTAGG,
    T1.DIZHHAGG,
    T1.BILDSNOR,
    T1.BILDSRID,
    T1.BILDSRIC,
    T1.BILDTINI,
    T1.BILDTFIN,
    T1.T64COPBC,
    T2.T64DESNO,
    T2.T64DSRID,
    T1.BILCD,
    T1.BAVTPBIL,
    T1.BAVNRREA,
    T1.BAVFOGIU,
    T1.BAVDENCG,
    T1.BAVNAZCG,
    T1.BAVDENDI,
    T1.WBSNRLOG,
    T1.WPBNRLOG,
    T1.ATTNE2,
    T1.BAVAPPGR,
    T1.BAVSOLIQ,
    T1.BAVSOUNI,
    T1.BAVALDIR,
    T1.ATTNEB,
    T1.T96CD,
    T1.SBCCSDBC,
    T3.SBCDSNOR,
    T3.SBCDSRID
FROM
      FINANCE.BCBILPT T1
         LEFT OUTER JOIN
         FINANCE.BCSBCPT T3
     ON  T1.T01CD = T3.T01CD AND
         T1.SBCCSDBC = T3.SBCCSDBC
         LEFT OUTER JOIN
         FINANCE.BBT64PT T2
     ON  T1.T01CD = T2.T01CD AND
         T1.T64COPBC = T2.T64COPBC

    T1.T01CD,

    T1.DIZUTCRE,

    T1.DIZHHCRE,
    T1.DIZUTAGG,
    T1.DIZDTAGG,

    T1.BILDTFIN,
    T1.T64COPBC,
    T2.T64DESNO,
    T2.T64DSRID,
    T1.BILCD,
    T1.BAVTPBIL,
    T1.BAVNRREA,
    T1.BAVFOGIU,
    T1.BAVDENCG,
    T1.BAVNAZCG,
    T1.BAVDENDI,

    T1.WPBNRLOG,

    T3.SBCDSRID
FROM
      FINANCE.BCBILPT T1
         LEFT OUTER JOIN
         FINANCE.BCSBCPT T3
     ON  T1.T01CD = T3.T01CD AND
         T1.SBCCSDBC = T3.SBCCSDBC
         LEFT OUTER JOIN
         FINANCE.BBT64PT T2
     ON  T1.T01CD = T2.T01CD AND
         T1.T64COPBC = T2.T64COPBC

Elaborazione file comandi K:\ThipRil\CUM\5.0.0\fix\V4R8M0/39484/primrose/script/02Viste.TDDML.
DROP VIEW FINANCE.BBANIV2 
CREATE VIEW FINANCE.BBANIV2 (
    ANACD,
    ANICD,
    ANIRASOC,
    ANIRASO2,
    ANIINDIR,
    ANIINDI2,
    ANILOCAL,
    T34CD,
    T35CD,
    T35DSNOR,
    ANICAP,
    ANITELEF,
    ANITELEX,
    ANIFAX,
    ANICOEDI,
    ANIININT,
    ANINOTEL,
    ANIDFPA,
    ANIIPEC,
    DIZSTATO
) AS

SELECT
    T1.ANACD,
    T1.ANICD,
    T1.ANIRASOC,
    T1.ANIRASO2,
    T1.ANIINDIR,
    T1.ANIINDI2,
    T1.ANILOCAL,
    T1.T34CD,
    T1.T35CD,
    T2.T35DSNOR,
    T1.ANICAP,
    T1.ANITELEF,
    T1.ANITELEX,
    T1.ANIFAX,
    T1.ANICOEDI,
    T1.ANIININT,
    T1.ANINOTEL,
    T1.ANIDFPA,
    T1.ANIIPEC,
    T1.DIZSTATO
FROM
      FINANCE.BBANIPT T1
         LEFT OUTER JOIN
         FINANCE.BBT35PT T2
     ON  T1.T34CD = T2.T34CD AND
         T1.T35CD = T2.T35CD
    

DROP VIEW FINANCE.BBANIVA 
CREATE VIEW FINANCE.BBANIVA (
    ANACD,
    ANICD,
    ANIRASOC,
    ANIRASO2,
    ANIINDIR,
    ANIINDI2,
    ANILOCAL,
    T34CD,
    T35CD,
    T35DSNOR,
    ANICAP,
    ANITELEF,
    ANITELEX,
    ANIFAX,
    ANICOEDI,
    ANIININT,
    ANINOTEL,
    DIZSTATO
) AS

SELECT
    T1.ANACD,
    T1.ANICD,
    T1.ANIRASOC,
    T1.ANIRASO2,
    T1.ANIINDIR,
    T1.ANIINDI2,
    T1.ANILOCAL,
    T1.T34CD,
    T1.T35CD,
    T2.T35DSNOR,
    T1.ANICAP,
    T1.ANITELEF,
    T1.ANITELEX,
    T1.ANIFAX,
    T1.ANICOEDI,
    T1.ANIININT,
    T1.ANINOTEL,
    T1.DIZSTATO
FROM
      FINANCE.BBANIPT T1
         LEFT OUTER JOIN
         FINANCE.BBT35PT T2
     ON  T1.T34CD = T2.T34CD AND
         T1.T35CD = T2.T35CD

    ANACD,

    ANIRASO2,

    ANIINDI2,

    ANICAP,
    ANITELEF,
    ANITELEX,
    ANIFAX,
    ANICOEDI,
    ANIININT,
    ANINOTEL,
    DIZSTATO

    T1.ANACD,
    T1.ANICD,
    T1.ANIRASOC,
    T1.ANIRASO2,
    T1.ANIINDIR,
    T1.ANIINDI2,

CREATE VIEW THIP.IMPLOSIONE_V01 AS 
SELECT 
    MODPRO.ID_AZIENDA,MODPRO.ID_MODELLO,MODPRO.R_STABILIMENTO,MODPRO.DOMINIO,MODPRO.PRIORITA,MODPRO.R_ARTICOLO,MODPRO.R_COMMESSA,MODPRO.DESCRIZIONE,MODPRO.DESCR_RIDOTTA,MODPRO.TIPO_MODELLO,MODPRO.LOTTO_MINIMO,MODPRO.LOTTO_MULTIPLO,MODPRO.LOTTO_MASSIMO,MODPRO.LOTTO_ATTREZ,MODPRO.TEMPO_APV_LOT_MIN,MODPRO.TEMPO_APV_LOT_MUL,MODPRO.TEMPI_PIANIF_APV,MODPRO.TEMPO_ANT_FAB,MODPRO.QUANTITA_BASE,MODPRO.R_MAGAZZINO_VRS,MODPRO.R_MAGAZZINO_PRL,MODPRO.R_TIPO_CIC_STD,MODPRO.R_POLIT_RIORD,MODPRO.DATA_DISPON,MODPRO.DATA_AGGIOR,MODPRO.R_RESPONSABILE,MODPRO.R_DOCUMENTO_MM,MODPRO.R_GES_COMMENTI,MODPRO.STATO,MODPRO.R_UTENTE_AGG,MODPRO.R_UTENTE_CRZ,MODPRO.TIMESTAMP_CRZ,MODPRO.TIMESTAMP_AGG,MODPRO.R_MAGAZZINO_WIP,MODPRO.METODO_RES_ORD,MODPRO.R_CLIENTE,MODPRO.NUM_PAR_LOT_MAX, MODPRO.STATO_COMPLETAM_ORD,
    M_ARTICOLI.ID_ARTICOLO      AS M_ID_ARTICOLO, 
    M_ARTICOLI.DESCRIZIONE      AS M_ART_DESCRIZIONE, 
    M_ARTICOLI.DESCR_RIDOTTA    AS M_ART_DESCR_RIDOTTA,

    M_ARTICOLI.EREDITA_CFG      AS M_EREDITA_CFG, 
    M_ARTICOLI.R_CONFIG_STD     AS M_R_CONFIG_STD, 
    M_ARTICOLI.GES_SALDI_COMMES AS M_GES_SALDI_COMM, 
    M_ARTICOLI.QTA_INTERA       AS M_QTA_INTERA, 
    MODPRO_ATV.ID_RIGA_ATTIVITA, 
    MODPRO_ATV.DESCRIZIONE   AS ATV_DESC, 
    MODPRO_ATV.DESCR_RIDOTTA AS ATV_DESC_R, 
    MODPRO_ATV.R_ATTIVITA, 
    MODPRO_ATV.R_OPERAZIONE, 
    MODPRO_ATV.R_CENTRO_LAVORO, 
    MODPRO_ATV.R_CENTRO_COSTO, 
    MODPRO_ATV.R_ATTREZZAGGIO, 
    MODPRO_ATV.SOG_COLLAUDO, 
    MODPRO_ATV.BUFFER_ANTICIPO, 
    MODPRO_ATV.TEMPO_SOVRAP, 
    MODPRO_ATV.QUANTITA_SOVRAP, 
    MODPRO_ATV.NUM_PARALLELISMO, 
    MODPRO_ATV.LOTTO_MOVIM, 
    MODPRO_ATV.REINTEGRO_SCARTO, 
    MODPRO_ATV.PERCEN_SCARTO, 
    MODPRO_ATV.TIPO_CRIT_VALID, 
    MODPRO_ATV.DATA_INZ_VALID, 
    MODPRO_ATV.DATA_FIN_VALID, 
    MODPRO_ATV.R_VER_INZ_VALID, 
    MODPRO_ATV.R_VER_FIN_VALID, 
    MODPRO_ATV.R_REGOLA, 
    MODPRO_ATV.TIPI_CICLO_AMM, 
    MODPRO_ATV.SINTESI_TIPI_CICLO, 
    MODPRO_ATV.VINCOLO_DATA_PGM, 
    MODPRO_ATV.POL_CONS_ATTIV, 
    MODPRO_ATV.STP_BOLLA_LAV, 
    MODPRO_ATV.STP_BOLLA_PRL, 
    MODPRO_ATV.STP_BOLLA_VRS, 
    MODPRO_ATV.STP_TAGLND_IDENT, 
    MODPRO_ATV.R_GES_COMMENTI AS ATV_GES_COMM, 
    MODPRO_ATV.R_DOCUMENTO_MM AS ATV_DOC_MM, 
    MODPRO_ATV.ATV_INIZIALE, 
    MODPRO_ATV.ATV_FINALE, 
    MODPRO_ATV.STATO         AS ATV_STATO, 
    MODPRO_ATV.R_UTENTE_CRZ  AS ATV_UT_CR, 
    MODPRO_ATV.TIMESTAMP_CRZ AS ATV_TS_CR, 
    MODPRO_ATV.TIMESTAMP_AGG AS ATV_TS_AGG,

    MODPRO_ATV_MAT.R_UM_DIMENSIONI, 
    MODPRO_ATV_MAT.LUNGHEZZA, 
    MODPRO_ATV_MAT.LARGHEZZA, 
    MODPRO_ATV_MAT.ALTEZZA, 
    MODPRO_ATV_MAT.COEFF_TAGLIO, 
    MODPRO_ATV_MAT.BUFFER_ANTICIPO AS MAT_BUF_ANT, 
    MODPRO_ATV_MAT.MOD_PRELIEVO, 
    MODPRO_ATV_MAT.R_MAGAZZINO_PRL AS MAT_MAG_PRL, 
    MODPRO_ATV_MAT.R_ARTICOLO_ALT, 
    MODPRO_ATV_MAT.NOTE, 
    MODPRO_ATV_MAT.STATO         AS MAT_STATO, 
    MODPRO_ATV_MAT.R_UTENTE_AGG  AS MAT_UT_AGG, 
    MODPRO_ATV_MAT.R_UTENTE_CRZ  AS MAT_UT_CRZ, 
    MODPRO_ATV_MAT.TIMESTAMP_CRZ AS MAT_TS_CRZ, 
    MODPRO_ATV_MAT.TIMESTAMP_AGG AS MAT_TS_AGG, 
    MODPRO_ATV_MAT.ESPONI_IN_BOLLA, 
    MODPRO_ATV_MAT.APPLIC_ANTICIPO, 
    MODPRO_ATV_MAT.IDENTIF_BENE  AS IDENTIF_BENE, 
    MODPRO_ATV_MAT.ADDEBITO_SER  AS ADDEBITO_SER, 
    MODPRO_ATV_MAT.RIFERIMENTO   AS RIFERIMENTO, 
    MODPRO_ATV_MAT.R_SCHEMA_CFG  AS R_SCHEMA_COEFF, 
    MODPRO_ATV_MAT.R_MACRO_COEFF AS R_MACRO_COEFF, 
    MODPRO_ATV_MAT.ESCLUSO_COSTI AS ESCLUSO_COSTI, 
    MODPRO_ATV_MAT.COSTO_LOT_ATTREZ AS COSTO_LOT_ATTREZ, 
	MODPRO_ATV_MAT.TIPI_CICLO_AMM AS MAT_TP_CIC_AMM, 
    MODPRO_ATV_MAT.SINTESI_TIPI_CICLO AS MAT_SINT_TP_CIC,
    MODPRO_ATV_MAT.R_MAGAZZINO_RFR AS R_MAGAZZINO_RFR,
    ARTICOLI.ID_ARTICOLO         AS ID_ARTICOLO, 
    ARTICOLI.DESCRIZIONE         AS ART_DESCRIZIONE, 
    ARTICOLI.DESCR_RIDOTTA       AS ART_DESCR_RIDOTTA, 
    ARTICOLI.TIPO_PARTE          AS TIPO_PARTE, 
    ARTICOLI.R_GRP_MODELLO       AS R_GRP_MODELLO, 
    ARTICOLI.R_UM_TECNICA        AS R_UM_TECNICA, 
    ARTICOLI.R_UM_PRM_MAG        AS R_UM_PRM_MAG, 
    ARTICOLI.R_CATEGORIA_UM      AS R_CATEGORIA_UM, 
    ARTICOLI.R_SCHEMA_CFG        AS R_SCHEMA_CFG, 
    ARTICOLI.EREDITA_CFG         AS EREDITA_CFG, 
    ARTICOLI.R_CONFIG_STD        AS R_CONFIG_STD, 
    ARTICOLI.GES_SALDI_COMMES    AS GES_SALDI_COMMES, 
    ARTICOLI.QTA_INTERA          AS QTA_INTERA,
    M_ARTICOLI.GES_VERSIONI AS GES_VERSIONI,
    M_ARTICOLI.ID_PRODOTTO_FMT AS M_ID_PRODOTTO_FMT,
    M_ARTICOLI.DESCR_ESTESA AS M_DESCR_ESTESA,
    M_ARTICOLI.STATO AS M_STATO_ARTICOLO,
    ARTICOLI.ID_PRODOTTO_FMT AS ID_PRODOTTO_FMT,
    ARTICOLI.DESCR_ESTESA AS DESCR_ESTESA,
    ARTICOLI.STATO AS STATO_ARTICOLO
FROM THIP.MODPRO MODPRO,THIP.ARTICOLI M_ARTICOLI,THIP.MODPRO_ATV MODPRO_ATV,THIP.MODPRO_ATV_MAT MODPRO_ATV_MAT,THIP.ARTICOLI ARTICOLI 
WHERE 
    MODPRO.ID_AZIENDA               = M_ARTICOLI.ID_AZIENDA 
    AND MODPRO.ID_AZIENDA           = MODPRO_ATV.ID_AZIENDA 
    AND MODPRO.ID_AZIENDA           = MODPRO_ATV_MAT.ID_AZIENDA 
    AND MODPRO.ID_AZIENDA           = ARTICOLI.ID_AZIENDA 
    AND MODPRO.R_ARTICOLO           = M_ARTICOLI.ID_ARTICOLO 
    AND MODPRO.ID_MODELLO           = MODPRO_ATV.ID_MODELLO 
    AND MODPRO.ID_MODELLO           = MODPRO_ATV_MAT.ID_MODELLO 
    AND MODPRO_ATV.ID_RIGA_ATTIVITA = MODPRO_ATV_MAT.ID_RIGA_ATTIVITA 
    AND MODPRO_ATV_MAT.R_ARTICOLO   = ARTICOLI.ID_ARTICOLO

DROP TABLE FINANCE.BTMLCPT
#WARNING#
Non è possibile eliminare l'oggetto 'FINANCE.BTMLCPT' di tipo tabella, perché inesistente o perché non si dispone dell'autorizzazione.


CREATE TABLE FINANCE.BTMLCPT
(
   T01CD CHAR(3) NOT NULL,
   T40CD CHAR(5) NOT NULL,
   TMLTNRIF CHAR(10) NOT NULL,
   TMLDTPRA CHAR(1) NOT NULL,
   TMLDNRRA NUMERIC(7,0) NOT NULL,
   TMLDPROG NUMERIC(7,0) NOT NULL,
   MOCPROV CHAR(1) NOT NULL,
   MOVDINCO DATETIME,
   MOVDFICO DATETIME,
   MOVDTRCO DATETIME,
   MOCT02CD CHAR(3),
   MOCVOCCD CHAR(12)
)  ON 'FINANCE4'
ALTER TABLE FINANCE.BTMLCPT ADD CONSTRAINT BTMLCPT_IX PRIMARY KEY (T01CD, T40CD, TMLTNRIF, TMLDTPRA, TMLDNRRA, TMLDPROG, MOCPROV )
GRANT ALL ON FINANCE.BTMLCPT TO PUBLIC
DROP TABLE FINANCE.BTMOCPT
#WARNING#
Non è possibile eliminare l'oggetto 'FINANCE.BTMOCPT' di tipo tabella, perché inesistente o perché non si dispone dell'autorizzazione.


CREATE TABLE FINANCE.BTMOCPT
(
   T01CD CHAR(3) NOT NULL,
   T09CD CHAR(3) NOT NULL,
   TTMOTNMO NUMERIC(7,0) NOT NULL,
   TTMOVPRG NUMERIC(7,0) NOT NULL,
   MOCPROV CHAR(1) NOT NULL,
   MOVDINCO DATETIME,
   MOVDFICO DATETIME,
   MOVDTRCO DATETIME,
   MOCT02CD CHAR(3),
   MOCVOCCD CHAR(12)
)  ON 'FINANCE4'
ALTER TABLE FINANCE.BTMOCPT ADD CONSTRAINT BTMOCPT_IX PRIMARY KEY (T01CD, T09CD, TTMOTNMO, TTMOVPRG, MOCPROV )
GRANT ALL ON FINANCE.BTMOCPT TO PUBLIC

Elaborazione file comandi K:\ThipRil\CUM\5.0.0\fix\V4R8M0/39597/primrose/script/02Viste.TDDML.
DROP VIEW FINANCE.BTMLCV2 
#WARNING#
Non è possibile eliminare l'oggetto 'FINANCE.BTMLCV2' di tipo vista, perché inesistente o perché non si dispone dell'autorizzazione.


CREATE VIEW FINANCE.BTMLCV2 (
    T01CD,
    T40CD,
    TMLTNRIF,
    TMLDTPRA,
    TMLDNRRA,
    TMLDPROG,
    MOCPROV,
    MOVDINCO,
    MOVDFICO,
    MOVDTRCO,
    MOCT02CD,
    MOCT02DE,
    MOCT02DR,
    MOCVOCCD,
    MOCVOCDE,
    MOCVOCDR
) AS

SELECT
    T1.T01CD,
    T1.T40CD,
    T1.TMLTNRIF,
    T1.TMLDTPRA,
    T1.TMLDNRRA,
    T1.TMLDPROG,
    T1.MOCPROV,
    T1.MOVDINCO,
    T1.MOVDFICO,
    T1.MOVDTRCO,
    T1.MOCT02CD,
    T2.T02DSNOR,
    T2.T02DSRID,
    T1.MOCVOCCD,
    T3.VOCDSNOR,
    T3.VOCDSRID
FROM
      FINANCE.BTMLCPT T1
         LEFT OUTER JOIN
         FINANCE.BBVOCPT T3
     ON  T1.T01CD = T3.T01CD AND
         T1.MOCVOCCD = T3.VOCCD
         LEFT OUTER JOIN
         FINANCE.BBT02PT T2
     ON  T1.T01CD = T2.T01CD AND
         T1.MOCT02CD = T2.T02CD

    T1.T01CD,
    T1.T40CD,
    T1.TMLTNRIF,
    T1.TMLDTPRA,
    T1.TMLDNRRA,
    T1.TMLDPROG,
    T1.MOCPROV,
    T1.MOVDINCO,
    T1.MOVDFICO,
    T1.MOVDTRCO,
    T1.MOCT02CD,
    T2.T02DSNOR,
    T2.T02DSRID,
    T1.MOCVOCCD,
    T3.VOCDSNOR,
    T3.VOCDSRID
FROM
      FINANCE.BTMLCPT T1
         LEFT OUTER JOIN
         FINANCE.BBVOCPT T3
     ON  T1.T01CD = T3.T01CD AND
         T1.MOCVOCCD = T3.VOCCD
         LEFT OUTER JOIN
         FINANCE.BBT02PT T2

    T1.T40CD,
    T1.TMLTNRIF,
    T1.TMLDTPRA,
    T1.TMLDNRRA,
    T1.TMLDPROG,
    T1.MOCPROV,
    T1.MOVDINCO,
    T1.MOVDFICO,
    T1.MOVDTRCO,
    T1.MOCT02CD,
    T2.T02DSNOR,
    T2.T02DSRID,
    T1.MOCVOCCD,
    T3.VOCDSNOR,
    T3.VOCDSRID
FROM
      FINANCE.BTMLCPT T1
         LEFT OUTER JOIN
         FINANCE.BBVOCPT T3
     ON  T1.T01CD = T3.T01CD AND
         T1.MOCVOCCD = T3.VOCCD

    T1.TMLDTPRA,
    T1.TMLDNRRA,
    T1.TMLDPROG,
    T1.MOCPROV,
    T1.MOVDINCO,
    T1.MOVDFICO,
    T1.MOVDTRCO,
    T1.MOCT02CD,
    T2.T02DSNOR,
    T2.T02DSRID,
    T1.MOCVOCCD,
    T3.VOCDSNOR,
    T3.VOCDSRID
FROM
      FINANCE.BTMLCPT T1
         LEFT OUTER JOIN
         FINANCE.BBVOCPT T3
     ON  T1.T01CD = T3.T01CD AND
         T1.MOCVOCCD = T3.VOCCD
         LEFT OUTER JOIN
         FINANCE.BBT02PT T2
     ON  T1.T01CD = T2.T01CD AND
         T1.MOCT02CD = T2.T02CD

DROP VIEW FINANCE.THPSVV4
CREATE VIEW FINANCE.THPSVV4 AS 
SELECT 
T1.ID_AZIENDA, 
T1.ANNO_FAT, 
T1.NUMERO_FATTURA,

Elaborazione file comandi K:\ThipRil\CUM\5.0.0\fix\V4R8M0/39970/primrose/script/01Viste.TDDML.
DROP VIEW FINANCE.THMOTVL_V1
CREATE VIEW FINANCE.THMOTVL_V1 AS 
		SELECT 
			T2.T01CD,T2.T09CD, T1.TACQANFI, T1.TACQNRFT, T1.TRAIIVVE, T2.MOVAAPAR TACQANPC,
			T2.MOVNUREG,T2.MOVTCLFO, T2.MOVSTATO, T2.DIZUTCRE, T2.DIZDTCRE, T2.DIZHHCRE, T2.DIZUTAGG, 
			T2.DIZDTAGG, T2.DIZHHAGG, T2.MOVTPVAL, T2.T04CD, T2.T15CD, T2.MOVDTRCO, 	
			T2.MOVDTCOM,T2.MOVDTIVA, T2.MOVDTDOC, T2.MOVDTOPE, T2.MOVDTCOA,	T2.MOVDTSPA,T2.MOVNRPAR, 
			T2.T29CD, T2.MOVCAMBVP, T2.MOVTICAU, T2.MOVDSCAU, T2.MOVDSAGG, T2.MOVCAMBVS, T2.T02CD, T2.T02DSNOR, 
			T2.T02DSRID, T2.T22CD, T2.T22DSNOR, T2.T22DSRID, T2.T36CD, T2.T30CD, COALESCE(T1.NUMDOC, T3.NUMDOC, T2.MOVNDORI) AS MOVNDORI, T2.MOVNUPRA, 
			T2.T40CD,T2.CLICD, T2.CLIDSRID, T2.CLIRASOC, T2.FORCD, T2.FORRASOC, T2.FORDSRID, T2.VOCCD, 	
			T2.VOCDSNOR,T2.VOCDSRID, T2.T16CD, T2.T23CD, T2.T17CD, T2.T07CD, T2.MOVNPIVA,T2.MOVIVADF, 
			T2.FORSOFAC, T2.MOVVPDIM, T2.MOVVSDIM, T2.MOVVEDIM, T2.MOVINUSO,T2.MOVDTVAL, T2.FOBNPROG, T2.CLBNPROG, MOVABCAB, 
			T2.T39CD, T2.T38CDABI, T2.T38CDCAB, T2.MOVNCCOR, T2.MOVCCIN, T2.MOVBIC, T2.MOVIBAN, T2.T97CD, 
			CASE WHEN T1.TACQANFI IS NOT NULL THEN T1.TACQANFI ELSE T2.ANNO_DOC END AS ANNO_DOC, 
			CASE WHEN T1.TACQNRFT IS NOT NULL THEN T1.TACQNRFT ELSE T2.NUM_DOC_FORM END AS NUM_DOC_FORM, 
			T2.MOVSTRREG, 
                	COALESCE(TIPO_DOCUMENTO_SDI, ' ') AS TPDOCSDI
		FROM FINANCE.THMOTVL T2 
		LEFT OUTER JOIN FINANCE.THACQVL T1 ON 
			T1.T01CD = T2.T01CD AND 
			T1.T09CD = T2.T09CD AND 
			T1.TRANREGG = T2.MOVNUREG
                LEFT OUTER JOIN FINANCE.BCMFEPT T3 ON 
			T3.T01CD = T2.T01CD AND 
			T3.T09CD = T2.T09CD AND 
			T3.MOVNUREG = T2.MOVNUREG
                LEFT OUTER JOIN THIP.FATTURE_ACQUISTO T4 ON 
			T4.KEYPRGINVIO = T3.KEYINVIO AND 
			T4.KEYHEADERFATT = T3.KEY1FATT AND 
			T4.KEYBODYFATT = T3.KEY2FATT

    T30DSRIC,
    T30DSRID,
    ANACD,
    ANARASOC,
    ANADSRID,
    FORCD,
    FORRASOC,
    FORDSRID,
    MT03CD,
    MT03DSNO,
    MT03DSBR,
    MAGECHCP,
    MAGEDTIN,
    MAGEDTFI,
    MAGEMATR,
    MAGENRRU,
    MAGEPLIQ,
    MAGETPCT,
    T02CD,
    T02DSNOR,
    T02DSRID,
    MAGENC,
    MAG1DN01,
    MAGDSR01,
    MAGELNC,
    MAGEABLC,
    MAGEACSS
) AS

SELECT
    T1.T01CD,
    T1.DIZSTATO,
    T1.DIZUTCRE,
    T1.DIZDTCRE,
    T1.DIZHHCRE,
    T1.DIZUTAGG,
    T1.DIZDTAGG,
    T1.DIZHHAGG,
    T1.T30CD,
    T2.T30DSNOR,
    T2.T30DSRIC,
    T2.T30DSRID,
    T1.ANACD,
    T3.ANARASOC,
    T3.ANADSRID,
    T1.FORCD,
    T4.FORRASOC,
    T4.FORDSRID,
    T1.MT03CD,
    T5.MT03DSNO,
    T5.MT03DSBR,
    T1.MAGECHCP,
    T1.MAGEDTIN,
    T1.MAGEDTFI,
    T1.MAGEMATR,
    T1.MAGENRRU,
    T1.MAGEPLIQ,
    T1.MAGETPCT,
    T1.T02CD,
    T6.T02DSNOR,
    T6.T02DSRID,
    T1.MAGENC,
    T7.T02DSNOR,
    T7.T02DSRID,
    T1.MAGELNC,
    T1.MAGEABLC,
    T1.MAGEACSS
FROM
      FINANCE.BMAGEPT T1
         LEFT OUTER JOIN
         FINANCE.BBT02PT T7
     ON  T1.T01CD = T7.T01CD AND
         T1.MAGENC = T7.T02CD
         LEFT OUTER JOIN
         FINANCE.BBT02PT T6
     ON  T1.T01CD = T6.T01CD AND
         T1.T02CD = T6.T02CD
         LEFT OUTER JOIN
         FINANCE.BMT03PT T5
     ON  T1.T01CD = T5.T01CD AND
         T1.MT03CD = T5.MT03CD
         LEFT OUTER JOIN
         FINANCE.BBFORPT T4
     ON  T1.T01CD = T4.T01CD AND
         T1.FORCD = T4.FORCD
         LEFT OUTER JOIN
         FINANCE.BBANAPT T3
     ON  T1.ANACD = T3.ANACD
         LEFT OUTER JOIN
         FINANCE.BBT30PT T2
     ON  T1.T01CD = T2.T01CD AND
         T1.T30CD = T2.T30CD

    T1.FORFVDIN,
    T1.FORTPVAL,

    T1.FORDSRIC,

    T1.FORRASOC,
    T1.FORDSRID,
    T1.FORDOGAN,
    T1.FORPROFE,
    T1.FORSOCFA,
    T1.FORPRAGE,
    T1.FORTICER,

      FINANCE.BBFORPT T1
         LEFT OUTER JOIN

     ON  T1.T01CD = T6.T01CD AND

         T1.T05CD = T3.T05CD
         LEFT OUTER JOIN
         FINANCE.BBT22PT T2
     ON  T1.T01CD = T2.T01CD AND
         T1.T22CD = T2.T22CD

UPDATE THERA.CLASS_HDR SET UPD_FROM_GRID = 'C' WHERE UPD_FROM_GRID = 'N'
UPDATE THERA.CLASSAD SET UPD_FROM_GRID = 'C' WHERE UPD_FROM_GRID = 'N' AND CLASS_NAME IN (SELECT h.CLASS_NAME FROM THERA.CLASS_HDR h JOIN THERA.CLASSAD a ON h.CLASS_NAME = a.CLASS_NAME WHERE h.UPD_FROM_GRID = 'C')
UPDATE THERA.CLASSCD SET UPD_FROM_GRID = 'C' WHERE UPD_FROM_GRID = 'N' AND CLASS_NAME IN (SELECT h.CLASS_NAME FROM THERA.CLASS_HDR h JOIN THERA.CLASSCD a ON h.CLASS_NAME = a.CLASS_NAME WHERE h.UPD_FROM_GRID = 'C')

CREATE TABLE THERA.PIVOT_DATA_HDR
(
   ID INTEGER NOT NULL,
   SETTING_KEY INTEGER NOT NULL,
   PIVOT_KEY INTEGER NOT NULL,
   CLASS_NAME CHAR(25) NOT NULL,
   TIMESTAMP DATETIME NOT NULL DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP,
CONSTRAINT PVTDTAH2PVTTBL FOREIGN KEY (SETTING_KEY, PIVOT_KEY)
        REFERENCES THERA.PIVOT_TABLE ON DELETE CASCADE
)  ON 'THIP4'
CREATE UNIQUE INDEX PIVOT_DATA_HDR_I01 ON THERA.PIVOT_DATA_HDR (ID ASC)
CREATE INDEX PIVOT_DATA_HDR_I02 ON THERA.PIVOT_DATA_HDR (ID ASC, TIMESTAMP ASC)
ALTER TABLE THERA.PIVOT_DATA_HDR ADD PRIMARY KEY  (ID)
GRANT ALL ON THERA.PIVOT_DATA_HDR TO PUBLIC
